propertiesForSale.description:
Espace Real Estate is delighted to bring to the market this upgraded type 17 villa in a quiet location within Mirador. The villa is situated opposite the pool and parks in a cul-de-sac, with a large plot which has plenty of space for entertaining and a private pool. Inside, the property has been fully upgraded, the kitchen has been changed and opened up. Downstairs has a high-vaulted ceiling, a popular feature of this type, with a separate family room to the rear, next to the kitchen. There is a guest room and bathroom on the ground floor, with 4 other bedrooms upstairs. The master and one other bedroom are with an en-suite and a family bathroom for the other two rooms.
